                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Russell</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-02-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 7, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Root states that the embassy at Paris has been cabled to instruct consuls to
                    take charge of archives of Venezuelan consulates, if agreeable to the Government
                    of France.)</p>
            </div>
